        <div class="pf-duration-card"><div class="pf-duration-time">5–7 hrs</div><div><strong>Standard system, 3 to 4 bed, 8 to 12 radiators</strong><p>The most common Liverpool property type. According to <a href="https://boilercentral.com/guides/what-does-a-power-flush-do/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Boiler Central</a>, a 3-bed house with a moderately contaminated system typically takes around 6 hours.</p></div></div>
